1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:01,000


2
00:01:43,571 --> 00:01:44,851
=Light Beyond the Reed=

3
00:01:44,851 --> 00:01:47,410
(Adapted from the Jinjiang novel
"Light Beyond the Reed" by Mo Shubai)

4
00:01:48,220 --> 00:01:51,220
=Episode 17=

5
00:01:55,800 --> 00:01:57,333
Captain Zhang wants to talk to you.

6
00:02:01,490 --> 00:02:02,330
Hello?

7
00:02:02,930 --> 00:02:04,930
Were you planning
to kill Fan Jiancheng today?

8
00:02:05,311 --> 00:02:06,740
Qin Nan's going to do it for you.

9
00:02:06,955 --> 00:02:08,100
You need to tell me exactly

10
00:02:08,100 --> 00:02:09,010
what you planned.

11
00:02:09,010 --> 00:02:09,890
Where did he go?

12
00:02:11,780 --> 00:02:12,620
Answer me.

13
00:02:12,890 --> 00:02:13,730
Say something!

14
00:02:16,500 --> 00:02:17,940
Ye Sibei, you listen to me.

15
00:02:18,340 --> 00:02:20,450
That 20,000 yuan
you got back in your senior year

16
00:02:21,290 --> 00:02:22,380
was from Qin Nan.

17
00:02:23,170 --> 00:02:25,220
It was his father's death compensation.

18
00:02:25,850 --> 00:02:27,220
It was meant for his own education.

19
00:02:27,220 --> 00:02:28,170
He gave it to you.

20
00:02:28,730 --> 00:02:30,730
He's already given you

21
00:02:30,730 --> 00:02:31,660
half his life.

22
00:02:32,220 --> 00:02:33,780
Are you going to let him throw away

23
00:02:33,780 --> 00:02:35,060
the rest of it too?

24
00:02:36,380 --> 00:02:37,220
Ye Sibei.

25
00:02:37,380 --> 00:02:38,220
Talk to me.

26
00:02:38,422 --> 00:02:39,500
Outskirts of the city.

27
00:02:39,666 --> 00:02:41,890
An abandoned power plant
at the foot of Mount Suming.

28
00:02:42,220 --> 00:02:43,340
I'm sending you the location.

29
00:02:43,340 --> 00:02:45,940
Call Fan Jiancheng and tell him
not to go to the casino tonight.

30
00:02:50,100 --> 00:02:51,740
(Fan Jiancheng)

31
00:02:56,900 --> 00:02:58,820
(Sibei)

32
00:03:01,488 --> 00:03:02,620
I need to take this call.

33
00:03:06,220 --> 00:03:07,060
Sibei.

34
00:03:08,660 --> 00:03:09,500
What did you say?

35
00:03:10,820 --> 00:03:11,890
I'm going there now!

36
00:03:12,290 --> 00:03:13,130
What happened?

37
00:03:13,540 --> 00:03:14,450
It's my brother-in-law.

38
00:03:14,450 --> 00:03:15,890
He's going after Fan Jiancheng.

39
00:03:15,890 --> 00:03:16,890
She asked me to stop him.

40
00:03:17,220 --> 00:03:18,060
I'm coming with you.

41
00:03:18,780 --> 00:03:19,620
Come on!

42
00:03:26,220 --> 00:03:31,060
(Zhang Yong)
♪We said we'd forget before dawn♪

43
00:03:31,060 --> 00:03:33,410
♪But in the fields of flowers,
we made mistakes♪

44
00:03:33,410 --> 00:03:36,420
♪That embrace♪

45
00:03:36,420 --> 00:03:38,170
(Zhang Yong)
♪Turned into torment♪

46
00:03:38,170 --> 00:03:40,460
(Fan Jiancheng)

47
00:03:48,740 --> 00:03:50,980
(Zhao Shuhui)

48
00:03:59,290 --> 00:04:00,130
Hello?

49
00:04:00,410 --> 00:04:01,410
This is Zhang Yong.

50
00:04:01,890 --> 00:04:02,730
Captain Zhang.

51
00:04:04,540 --> 00:04:05,410
Where's Fan Jiancheng?

52
00:04:06,010 --> 00:04:07,410
I don't know where he is.

53
00:04:07,980 --> 00:04:09,450
He's not home.

54
00:04:09,577 --> 00:04:11,450
Listen to me.
He's not answering his phone.

55
00:04:11,450 --> 00:04:13,060
If you know where he is,
tell me right now.

56
00:04:13,060 --> 00:04:14,290
Your husband's in danger.

57
00:04:14,610 --> 00:04:15,450
If you can reach him,

58
00:04:15,450 --> 00:04:16,533
tell him to come home.

59
00:04:17,100 --> 00:04:17,780
Okay.

60
00:04:17,780 --> 00:04:19,100
I'll call him now.

61
00:04:19,100 --> 00:04:20,340
I'll call him.

62
00:04:20,900 --> 00:04:21,740
I'll call him.

63
00:04:25,620 --> 00:04:27,020
(Zhao Shuhui)

64
00:04:35,900 --> 00:04:37,060
(Zhao Shuhui)

65
00:04:50,540 --> 00:04:51,380
Drive carefully.

66
00:05:18,220 --> 00:05:19,060
(Sibei,)

67
00:05:20,000 --> 00:05:21,460
(I want you to do well.)

68
00:05:22,490 --> 00:05:23,900
(I want you to enjoy everything)

69
00:05:23,900 --> 00:05:25,220
(that I never could,)

70
00:05:25,730 --> 00:05:28,100
(and find the happiness I never found.)

71
00:05:29,850 --> 00:05:31,610
(I was drowning in my own struggles)

72
00:05:33,100 --> 00:05:34,460
(until something happened to you.)

73
00:05:37,020 --> 00:05:37,860
(At first,)

74
00:05:38,660 --> 00:05:40,170
(I thought it was duty,)

75
00:05:40,730 --> 00:05:42,410
(or maybe the part of me)

76
00:05:42,850 --> 00:05:45,020
(that couldn't accept
seeing you humiliated.)

77
00:05:47,980 --> 00:05:49,100
(But little by little,)

78
00:05:49,660 --> 00:05:50,930
(I started)

79
00:05:51,920 --> 00:05:53,460
(to feel something deeper.)

80
00:05:54,610 --> 00:05:56,170
(Maybe it was more than that.)

81
00:05:56,170 --> 00:05:57,220
Sibei!

82
00:05:57,220 --> 00:05:58,930
- (I've asked myself countless times)
- Sibei!

83
00:05:59,730 --> 00:06:01,220
- (why I stayed by your side.)
- Sibei!

84
00:06:01,377 --> 00:06:02,930
(Is it because you were a reflection)

85
00:06:02,930 --> 00:06:04,660
(of the hope I still had for the world?)

86
00:06:05,730 --> 00:06:06,570
(But)

87
00:06:08,100 --> 00:06:08,980
(when you asked me...)

88
00:06:09,490 --> 00:06:11,850
Could you really accept
what happened to me?

89
00:06:12,540 --> 00:06:14,170
Could you really love me?

90
00:06:17,100 --> 00:06:18,660
(That was when I realized,)

91
00:06:19,288 --> 00:06:21,490
(from the moment I began
to accept your weakness,)

92
00:06:21,900 --> 00:06:23,170
(to understand you,)

93
00:06:23,730 --> 00:06:25,370
(to share a life with you,)

94
00:06:27,250 --> 00:06:29,780
(to hear you yelling
on the back of my motorcycle,)

95
00:06:30,730 --> 00:06:33,100
(to watch the city lights together,)

96
00:06:34,488 --> 00:06:36,850
(you were no longer
just my faith or my cause.)

97
00:06:37,700 --> 00:06:39,780
(You were a real person.)

98
00:06:41,930 --> 00:06:44,140
(Someone I had poured
all my emotions into,)

99
00:06:44,900 --> 00:06:46,100
(whether it was love,)

100
00:06:46,900 --> 00:06:48,220
(or something beyond that.)

101
00:06:52,020 --> 00:06:52,860
(Sibei,)

102
00:06:54,170 --> 00:06:56,290
(most people think you're the weak one.)

103
00:06:57,290 --> 00:06:58,370
(But the truth is,)

104
00:06:59,780 --> 00:07:01,410
(the weak one was me.)

105
00:07:02,460 --> 00:07:04,370
(I gave in to fate over and over again,)

106
00:07:04,850 --> 00:07:07,140
(and accepted every future
it forced on me.)

107
00:07:08,140 --> 00:07:08,980
(But you,)

108
00:07:09,540 --> 00:07:10,810
(past)

109
00:07:11,140 --> 00:07:12,020
(and present,)

110
00:07:13,140 --> 00:07:14,460
(your soul never)

111
00:07:15,700 --> 00:07:17,460
(bowed to it.)

112
00:07:18,930 --> 00:07:20,290
(That's what I admired most,)

113
00:07:21,000 --> 00:07:22,622
(and what I loved most about you.)

114
00:07:25,050 --> 00:07:26,460
(So in this world,)

115
00:07:28,140 --> 00:07:29,410
(your being alive)

116
00:07:30,000 --> 00:07:32,580
(Life's better with you by my side.)
(means far more than mine.)

117
00:07:35,170 --> 00:07:36,410
(From here on...)

118
00:07:36,410 --> 00:07:38,260
(Life's better with you
by my side every day.)

119
00:07:38,340 --> 00:07:40,810
(I hope you live happily,)

120
00:07:41,290 --> 00:07:42,930
(with the world I could never have.)

121
00:08:06,050 --> 00:08:06,890
(And lastly,)

122
00:08:07,250 --> 00:08:08,100
(Sibei,)

123
00:08:09,930 --> 00:08:11,170
(whenever, wherever,)

124
00:08:12,460 --> 00:08:13,580
(whether you know it)

125
00:08:14,540 --> 00:08:15,700
(or not,)

126
00:08:17,050 --> 00:08:18,460
(please remember,)

127
00:08:19,410 --> 00:08:20,370
(there will always be)

128
00:08:21,460 --> 00:08:22,900
(someone who loves you.)

129
00:08:26,460 --> 00:08:27,810
(Like Qin Nan.)

130
00:08:31,860 --> 00:08:36,300
(Like Qin Nan.)

131
00:09:09,580 --> 00:09:12,180
♪The pain and torment♪

132
00:09:17,180 --> 00:09:18,940
♪All came from your mistakes♪

133
00:10:37,250 --> 00:10:38,090
Somebody!

134
00:10:39,910 --> 00:10:40,770
Somebody help me!

135
00:10:40,770 --> 00:10:41,700
Help!

136
00:10:51,180 --> 00:10:54,060
(Player, Banker)

137
00:10:54,060 --> 00:10:55,130
Please place your bets.

138
00:10:55,130 --> 00:10:56,980
(Banker)

139
00:11:02,370 --> 00:11:03,700
Trouble!

140
00:11:04,730 --> 00:11:06,010
We've got trouble!

141
00:11:11,490 --> 00:11:13,250
- What's going on?
- What's happening?

142
00:11:13,250 --> 00:11:14,355
Something's gone wrong?

143
00:11:16,730 --> 00:11:18,700
It never ends.

144
00:11:21,420 --> 00:11:23,250
You've got the nerve
to stir up trouble here?

145
00:11:23,890 --> 00:11:24,890
Get him!

146
00:11:27,850 --> 00:11:28,980
Take him down!

147
00:11:30,650 --> 00:11:31,490
Catch him!

148
00:11:57,730 --> 00:11:58,890
Screw you!

149
00:12:01,420 --> 00:12:02,260
Get up!

150
00:12:05,130 --> 00:12:06,130
Take this!

151
00:12:15,530 --> 00:12:17,490
Stay back!

152
00:12:21,850 --> 00:12:23,370
I'm looking for Fan Jiancheng.

153
00:12:24,130 --> 00:12:25,688
This has nothing to do with you.

154
00:12:30,700 --> 00:12:31,890
Stop chasing him!

155
00:12:31,890 --> 00:12:33,370
Don't you hear the sirens?

156
00:12:33,370 --> 00:12:34,333
Let's get out of here.

157
00:12:43,220 --> 00:12:44,100
(Police)

158
00:12:49,850 --> 00:12:50,820
Lock everything down!

159
00:12:54,111 --> 00:12:55,530
- Move! Stay put!
- Hurry up!

160
00:14:06,730 --> 00:14:07,570
Qin Nan.

161
00:14:08,340 --> 00:14:09,180
Qin Nan...

162
00:14:09,460 --> 00:14:10,460
Please stop...

163
00:14:10,460 --> 00:14:11,460
Please?

164
00:14:13,820 --> 00:14:14,660
Qin Nan...

165
00:14:15,530 --> 00:14:16,370
I was wrong.

166
00:14:16,730 --> 00:14:17,820
I was wrong, all right?

167
00:14:18,820 --> 00:14:19,660
I'll turn myself in.

168
00:14:20,820 --> 00:14:22,060
I'll give you money.

169
00:14:22,370 --> 00:14:23,850
Whatever you want, it's yours.

170
00:14:24,130 --> 00:14:24,970
Please, stop...

171
00:14:25,340 --> 00:14:26,130
I was wrong...

172
00:14:26,130 --> 00:14:27,820
I was wrong, Qin Nan.

173
00:14:27,820 --> 00:14:29,420
I don't believe you.

174
00:14:29,420 --> 00:14:30,700
I only believe myself.

175
00:14:35,580 --> 00:14:37,370
Apologize to Ye Sibei.

176
00:14:38,130 --> 00:14:39,130
Apologize to her!

177
00:14:39,130 --> 00:14:39,940
Okay, I'll say it!

178
00:14:39,940 --> 00:14:41,370
It's my fault! All my fault!

179
00:14:42,060 --> 00:14:43,530
She didn't frame you.

180
00:14:43,530 --> 00:14:44,700
She didn't frame me.

181
00:14:44,700 --> 00:14:45,730
You raped her!

182
00:14:45,730 --> 00:14:47,130
I raped her!

183
00:14:47,130 --> 00:14:47,820
I raped her.

184
00:14:47,820 --> 00:14:48,730
I drugged her.

185
00:14:49,060 --> 00:14:50,530
I thought she was weak and easy...

186
00:14:50,530 --> 00:14:51,340
She was timid.

187
00:14:51,340 --> 00:14:52,666
I thought she wouldn't report it.

188
00:14:52,850 --> 00:14:53,690
You two...

189
00:14:53,822 --> 00:14:55,250
You weren't even on good terms.

190
00:14:55,530 --> 00:14:56,060
And

191
00:14:56,060 --> 00:14:57,130
you were short on money.

192
00:14:57,340 --> 00:14:58,460
So I figured

193
00:14:58,460 --> 00:15:00,370
even if she did report it,
nothing would happen.

194
00:15:01,820 --> 00:15:02,730
Is that enough?

195
00:15:02,730 --> 00:15:03,570
Is that enough now?

196
00:15:06,130 --> 00:15:07,250
I was wrong...

197
00:15:07,250 --> 00:15:08,130
Qin Nan...

198
00:15:09,130 --> 00:15:09,970
I was wrong...

199
00:15:10,130 --> 00:15:11,530
You deserve to die.

200
00:15:11,530 --> 00:15:13,340
I don't deserve to die, Qin Nan!

201
00:15:14,250 --> 00:15:15,130
Is this necessary?

202
00:15:15,130 --> 00:15:17,060
All this for something so small?

203
00:15:17,060 --> 00:15:18,340
I just

204
00:15:18,340 --> 00:15:20,060
couldn't control myself!

205
00:15:21,130 --> 00:15:22,130
Qin Nan,

206
00:15:22,130 --> 00:15:23,130
calm down.

207
00:15:23,730 --> 00:15:24,570
Please calm down.

208
00:15:25,130 --> 00:15:27,130
Even an animal knows when to stop.

209
00:15:27,820 --> 00:15:29,820
You're worse than an animal!

210
00:15:29,820 --> 00:15:31,220
Yes, I'm worse than an animal.

211
00:15:31,220 --> 00:15:32,730
I'm nothing.

212
00:15:32,730 --> 00:15:34,370
Qin Nan...

213
00:15:35,940 --> 00:15:37,220
I'll turn myself in.

214
00:15:37,220 --> 00:15:38,580
I'll give you money.

215
00:15:38,580 --> 00:15:40,460
I'll give you everything.

216
00:15:40,460 --> 00:15:42,130
I have a wife and a kid.

217
00:15:42,130 --> 00:15:43,580
They depend on me.

218
00:15:44,060 --> 00:15:45,130
What a shame.

219
00:15:47,730 --> 00:15:48,570
I don't.

220
00:15:53,340 --> 00:15:54,180
Qin Nan!

221
00:16:07,060 --> 00:16:07,940
Ye Sibei asked me

222
00:16:08,460 --> 00:16:09,580
to pass a message to you.

223
00:16:10,940 --> 00:16:12,060
She's

224
00:16:12,060 --> 00:16:12,940
let it go.

225
00:16:14,060 --> 00:16:15,580
That's what she wanted me to tell you.

226
00:16:15,580 --> 00:16:16,940
She's let it go.

227
00:16:16,940 --> 00:16:19,060
She's not holding onto it anymore.

228
00:16:21,460 --> 00:16:22,460
I don't believe that.

229
00:16:23,700 --> 00:16:24,580
I know her.

230
00:16:25,530 --> 00:16:26,530
She can't let it go.

231
00:16:27,220 --> 00:16:29,370
I went to Mr. Yang's house today.

232
00:16:29,370 --> 00:16:31,460
I know everything about your past.

233
00:16:32,044 --> 00:16:33,580
And I told Sibei everything you did

234
00:16:33,580 --> 00:16:35,010
to help her.

235
00:16:35,530 --> 00:16:37,530
Just give me a bit more time, all right?

236
00:16:37,530 --> 00:16:39,530
The case is about to be reopened.

237
00:16:40,060 --> 00:16:41,488
You'll win this time.

238
00:16:41,644 --> 00:16:43,700
You don't need
to throw away the rest of your life.

239
00:16:43,700 --> 00:16:45,130
You don't need to, Qin Nan.

240
00:16:45,580 --> 00:16:46,420
Think about it.

241
00:16:47,266 --> 00:16:48,940
Ye Sibei is still waiting for you.

242
00:16:49,940 --> 00:16:52,010
If you go down this road,
what's she going to do?

243
00:16:54,700 --> 00:16:55,540
Captain Zhang,

244
00:16:57,580 --> 00:16:59,370
this is a turning point in her life.

245
00:17:00,130 --> 00:17:01,370
Even without Qin Nan,

246
00:17:02,460 --> 00:17:03,340
Ye Sibei will meet

247
00:17:03,340 --> 00:17:04,810
other people.

248
00:17:05,570 --> 00:17:07,010
But without justice,

249
00:17:07,940 --> 00:17:09,050
she'll spend her whole life

250
00:17:09,050 --> 00:17:10,530
doubting the world.

251
00:17:10,530 --> 00:17:12,460
The law will give you both that justice!

252
00:17:12,460 --> 00:17:13,530
I don't believe it!

253
00:17:13,955 --> 00:17:15,220
How many years will he get?

254
00:17:17,460 --> 00:17:19,050
How many?

255
00:17:19,730 --> 00:17:20,900
Whatever he's sentenced to,

256
00:17:21,066 --> 00:17:23,860
how could it ever compare
to what she has to carry for a lifetime?

257
00:17:23,860 --> 00:17:26,090
You think killing him
will make things right?

258
00:17:26,090 --> 00:17:26,930
Yes!

259
00:17:29,180 --> 00:17:31,010
If heaven won't deliver justice,

260
00:17:32,290 --> 00:17:33,420
then I will.

261
00:17:36,010 --> 00:17:36,900
No, no, no!

262
00:17:37,980 --> 00:17:39,180
Who asked you to?

263
00:17:42,420 --> 00:17:43,330
Who asked you to!

264
00:17:45,460 --> 00:17:46,300
Come here.

265
00:17:54,860 --> 00:17:55,700
Qin Nan.

266
00:17:57,420 --> 00:17:58,570
One assault

267
00:17:59,860 --> 00:18:01,220
won't ruin my life.

268
00:18:02,010 --> 00:18:03,140
One lost case,

269
00:18:04,010 --> 00:18:05,140
one failure,

270
00:18:05,570 --> 00:18:06,770
one insult...

271
00:18:07,220 --> 00:18:09,010
None of it will ruin me.

272
00:18:09,770 --> 00:18:11,860
The reason I was scared before,

273
00:18:11,860 --> 00:18:13,570
the reason I cared so much,

274
00:18:13,570 --> 00:18:15,660
was because deep down inside,

275
00:18:15,660 --> 00:18:17,860
there was no voice
telling me I was enough.

276
00:18:17,860 --> 00:18:19,660
I thought no one loved me.

277
00:18:20,730 --> 00:18:22,290
I thought no one

278
00:18:22,290 --> 00:18:24,330
had ever actually cared for me.

279
00:18:24,330 --> 00:18:27,010
So I kept denying myself.

280
00:18:27,010 --> 00:18:29,010
Until this happened.

281
00:18:29,010 --> 00:18:31,330
Whenever something happened,

282
00:18:31,330 --> 00:18:33,570
I couldn't face it.

283
00:18:33,570 --> 00:18:35,090
But today, I finally realized,

284
00:18:35,570 --> 00:18:36,860
that's not true.

285
00:18:36,860 --> 00:18:38,570
It's that I didn't love myself enough.

