I would defy my superior

571
00:36:55,130 --> 00:36:56,210
and offend the client.

572
00:36:57,010 --> 00:36:57,900
So,

573
00:36:58,940 --> 00:37:00,170
I chose to obey.

574
00:37:00,980 --> 00:37:03,380
(Have you ever gone out alone at night?)

575
00:37:03,380 --> 00:37:04,340
(Yes.)

576
00:37:04,340 --> 00:37:05,860
(Have you ever worn)

577
00:37:05,860 --> 00:37:07,820
(what you thought
was a beautiful outfit)

578
00:37:07,820 --> 00:37:09,420
(or a short skirt?)

579
00:37:10,170 --> 00:37:11,340
(Of course.)

580
00:37:11,340 --> 00:37:12,622
(Who doesn't love to look nice?)

581
00:37:13,130 --> 00:37:15,130
(At that time,
did you think about safety?)

582
00:37:17,010 --> 00:37:18,090
I don't quite understand.

583
00:37:18,690 --> 00:37:21,420
We could teach girls to protect

584
00:37:21,420 --> 00:37:22,980
themselves beforehand,

585
00:37:24,460 --> 00:37:26,860
but instead, people blame the victim

586
00:37:27,300 --> 00:37:28,650
only after the harm,

587
00:37:28,650 --> 00:37:30,940
saying it's because of her own behavior.

588
00:37:30,940 --> 00:37:32,780
You're right.

589
00:37:32,780 --> 00:37:34,010
We should give victims

590
00:37:34,010 --> 00:37:37,170
more support and encouragement,

591
00:37:37,170 --> 00:37:39,380
so they can stand up

592
00:37:39,380 --> 00:37:41,530
without burden

593
00:37:41,530 --> 00:37:42,610
to identify the perpetrator.

594
00:37:43,860 --> 00:37:45,420
The reason I am

595
00:37:46,260 --> 00:37:48,740
sitting here for this interview today

596
00:37:49,460 --> 00:37:51,570
is to tell, through your program,

597
00:37:52,130 --> 00:37:54,420
those girls like me

598
00:37:54,420 --> 00:37:56,490
who have experienced injustice,

599
00:37:59,300 --> 00:38:00,530
I am not the first,

600
00:38:01,900 --> 00:38:03,420
and probably not the last.

601
00:38:03,900 --> 00:38:05,090
(I chose to report it.)

602
00:38:05,940 --> 00:38:07,460
(It is a difficult path.)

603
00:38:07,780 --> 00:38:08,900
(The reason it is hard)

604
00:38:08,900 --> 00:38:11,210
(is that I hesitated at first.)

605
00:38:11,490 --> 00:38:12,380
(If at the start)

606
00:38:12,380 --> 00:38:14,740
(I had chosen to do drug tests,)

607
00:38:14,740 --> 00:38:16,300
(blood tests, and other checks,)

608
00:38:17,050 --> 00:38:19,490
(the results now
might be completely different.)

609
00:38:19,740 --> 00:38:22,340
I hope everyone can be stronger than me,

610
00:38:22,340 --> 00:38:23,860
braver than me,

611
00:38:24,570 --> 00:38:27,740
and never give up pursuing justice.

612
00:38:27,740 --> 00:38:28,980
Go Sibei!

613
00:38:28,980 --> 00:38:30,570
(Your courage is unmatched!)
We support you!

614
00:38:30,570 --> 00:38:32,170
Ye Sibei, we believe in you!

615
00:38:32,170 --> 00:38:33,422
Keep fighting. We can win, Sibei!

616
00:38:33,422 --> 00:38:34,610
We are always with you.

617
00:38:34,610 --> 00:38:39,050
- Go Sibei!
- Go Sibei!

618
00:38:39,050 --> 00:38:40,260
Thank you.

619
00:38:46,340 --> 00:38:47,460
Thank you all.

620
00:38:49,260 --> 00:38:50,249
(Brave, independent, confident,
uncompromising,)

621
00:38:50,250 --> 00:38:51,500
(never giving up, never silent,
thoughtful, not blind following.)

622
00:38:51,500 --> 00:38:55,220
(Believe in yourself!
Your potential is limitless!)

623
00:39:25,170 --> 00:39:26,340
Hello?

624
00:39:26,340 --> 00:39:28,130
Officer Lin, this is Chuchu.

625
00:39:29,050 --> 00:39:30,490
I have a situation to report.

626
00:39:34,010 --> 00:39:34,980
I want to surrender.

627
00:40:09,580 --> 00:40:14,340
♪There's a gray cloud in your eyes♪

628
00:40:16,320 --> 00:40:21,910
♪But I see a long letter
through the clouds♪

629
00:40:22,990 --> 00:40:29,160
♪You hide your emotions, staying silent♪

630
00:40:29,610 --> 00:40:34,680
♪I wish I could accompany you
back to the clear sky♪

631
00:40:36,200 --> 00:40:41,310
♪If I could capture your shadow♪

632
00:40:42,930 --> 00:40:48,280
♪I wouldn't mind wandering again♪

633
00:40:49,540 --> 00:40:55,930
♪Moreover, my light is in your life♪

634
00:40:56,250 --> 00:41:01,690
♪So I must trust in myself♪

635
00:41:02,280 --> 00:41:06,590
♪Please let me become you♪

636
00:41:06,760 --> 00:41:10,220
♪The secret that you can tell♪

637
00:41:10,220 --> 00:41:15,780
♪Becoming the gentle fragrance
that heals your past♪

638
00:41:15,780 --> 00:41:19,780
♪If fate insists on drenching you♪

639
00:41:20,070 --> 00:41:22,820
♪With a torrential downpour♪

640
00:41:23,220 --> 00:41:28,640
♪Don't be afraid, I am your soul's coat♪

641
00:41:28,940 --> 00:41:33,010
♪Please let me become you♪

642
00:41:33,480 --> 00:41:36,790
♪Believing in the proof of love♪

643
00:41:36,790 --> 00:41:42,420
♪Becoming the island
where every dream of yours rests♪

644
00:41:42,420 --> 00:41:46,580
♪Don't lament the lost scenery♪

645
00:41:46,870 --> 00:41:49,520
♪As time passes♪

646
00:41:50,170 --> 00:41:55,440
♪I will still be here♪

647
00:41:56,040 --> 00:42:02,990
♪Not forgetting to accompany you
to the edges of the rest of life♪

648
00:42:26,370 --> 00:42:28,690
(The long road has an end,
the remaining life is limited.)

649
00:42:28,690 --> 00:42:30,200
(Protect every woman with love.)
